ra enjoying her time away.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A second swimmer, Vieira'sOlympicteammate Gabriel Santos of the men's team, joined her on the unsanctioned escapade.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Santos_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9999963865517913, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Santos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Santos_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Santos_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Santos, however, only received a warning.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Reuters, Vieira's harsher punishment came because she also chose to challenge the team's formation.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.032796803928059e-12, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athlete Ana Carolina, in a disrespectful and aggressive manner, contested a technical decision made by the Brazilian National Swimming Team committee,\\\" the Brazilian Olympic Committee said in a Sunday statement.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9972667165066836, \"rank\": 0.0015188338172660192, \"text\": \"Swimming\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1022, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://db